            <li><a href="https://documentation.devexpress.com/CoreLibraries/9948/DevExpress-ORM-Tool/Examples/How-to-Implement-Custom-Functions-and-Criteria-in-LINQ-to-XPO">Implement Custom Functions and Criteria in LINQ to XPO.</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://documentation.devexpress.com/CoreLibraries/3239/DevExpress-ORM-Tool/Examples/How-to-Obtain-a-Collection-of-Persistent-Objects-by-a-Set-of-Their-IDs">Obtain a Collection of Persistent Objects by a Set of Their IDs.</a></li>
